title: Divine Interruptions | Joel Osteen

description:
Sometimes God allows delay in order to protect us. If that door closed, it's because He has something better on the way. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
